      "descriptions": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Potential segfault in the time crate (RUSTSEC-2020-0071). The affected functions set environment variables without synchronization; on Unix-like systems time::now/time::at/time::at_utc/time::tzset can segfault in multithreaded programs. Affects time 0.1.x."
        }
